Who: RODIMUS PRIME, SCOURGE, SCORPONOK, Kup, Tuscon, Nightshift

> Kup arrived to the area where Tucson was and he opened fire against Scouge and Scorponok.

Rodimus stopped short as he heard Kup open fire on Scorponok and
Scourge, his desire to keep Nightlight safe warring with his desire to
help his friends . . . well . . . ones who may once again be his
friends.

Setting Nightlight down out of the line of fire he peered around the
corner and then like Kup opened fire on Scourge and Scorponok!
